root: ^: Hey Colette... Don't you think the character in this comic looks a lot like you?
^Colette: Are you sure you don't know who gave this to you?
^Colette: Oh! Yes, yes! I'm alright! Strange, strange comic.
^Colette: Well, thank you for the comic! I'll make sure it finds its proper place.
^: Are you sure? I can help.
^Colette: You're very sweet, but don't worry, it's my job. You can stop by in a bit if you wanna check in.
^: Alright. I'll check in for sure.
